WEBVTT

00:00.070 --> 00:02.661
Let's learn the days of the week.

00:09.184 --> 00:11.247
Monday to Friday, I work.

00:16.011 --> 00:19.195
On Monday after work, I play soccer.

00:23.224 --> 00:26.068
Tuesday, I meet friends for lunch.

00:31.628 --> 00:34.584
Wednesday, I have my yoga class.

00:41.434 --> 00:44.745
Thursday night, I stay home and watch TV.

00:53.785 --> 00:55.751
Friday, I go out to dinner.

00:59.863 --> 01:01.504
TGIF!

01:01.777 --> 01:03.861
Thank God it's Friday!

01:08.803 --> 01:11.584
On the weekend, I like to go to cafes.

01:16.231 --> 01:18.367
Saturday, I go for a run.

01:23.053 --> 01:25.779
Sunday, I visit my family.

01:29.960 --> 01:31.534
This is my week.

